%% DG-403: Odeme Akis Sequence Diyagrami
%% Durum: DRAFT
%% Editor: https://mermaid.live
%% Aciklama: Siparis -> odeme -> onay -> kargo akisi
%% ---

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Client as Frontend
    participant API as API Server
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant PG as Odeme Saglayici<br/>(iyzico/Stripe)
    participant Email as Email Service
    participant Cargo as Kargo Sistemi

    User->>Client: "Siparis Ver" tikla
    Client->>API: POST /api/v1/orders {items, address_id}
    API->>DB: Stok kontrolu
    DB-->>API: Stok yeterli
    API->>DB: INSERT order (status: payment_pending)
    API->>API: Toplam hesapla (subtotal + shipping - discount)
    API->>PG: Create payment intent {amount, currency, order_id}
    PG-->>API: {payment_id, client_secret}
    API-->>Client: {order_id, client_secret, redirect_url}

    Client->>PG: 3D Secure sayfasi
    User->>PG: Kart bilgileri + OTP
    PG-->>Client: Odeme sonucu

    Note over PG, API: Webhook (guvenilir kanal)
    PG->>API: POST /webhooks/payment {event: payment.completed}
    API->>API: Webhook imza dogrula (HMAC)
    API->>DB: UPDATE order SET status='paid'
    API->>DB: UPDATE stock (decrement)
    API->>DB: INSERT payment record
    API->>Email: Siparis onay emaili
    Email-->>User: "Siparisininiz alindi #12345"

    Note over API, Cargo: Siparis hazirlama
    API->>Cargo: Gonderim talebi {order_id, address}
    Cargo-->>API: {tracking_number}
    API->>DB: UPDATE order SET status='shipped', tracking=...
    API->>Email: Kargo bildirim emaili
    Email-->>User: "Siparisininiz kargoya verildi"

    Note over Cargo, User: Teslimat
    Cargo->>API: Webhook: delivered
    API->>DB: UPDATE order SET status='delivered'
    API->>Email: Teslimat bildirimi
    Email-->>User: "Siparisininiz teslim edildi"
